{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "18", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "04", "M": "22", "S": "10"}}, "news": [{"title": "MMRDA starts land acquisition for \u2018Third Mumbai\u2019; consent process from April 27", "para": "MMRDA has begun land acquisition for 'Third Mumbai,' the Karnala-Sai-Chirner New Town, spanning 124 villages in Raigad. Landowners can opt for monetary compensation or land-based returns, including a land pooling model. This initiative aims to boost regional economic growth and establish a major technology and infrastructure hub.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/mmrda-launches-land-acquisition-for-ambitious-third-mumbai-project/130346662?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-235538/130346662.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Over 900 acres of Mhada layouts will be redeveloped across Mumbai", "para": "Mhada is set to redevelop a dozen layouts spanning 923 acres, aiming to rehabilitate over 75,000 residents within 5-10 years. Key projects like Charkop and Gorai layouts will soon seek state cabinet approval. The initiative also includes slum rehabilitation and a push for rental housing under the state housing policy.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/mumbais-mhada-redevelopment-plan-923-acres-to-transform-housing-for-over-75000-residents/130346609?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-189645/130346609.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Bombay HC says Mhada could use unclaimed Patra Chawl flats for public housing", "para": "Bombay High Court has set a deadline of April 30, 2026, for Goregaon Siddharth Nagar Sahakari Griha Nirman Sanstha Limited society members to take possession of their tenements. If members fail to do so, the court will allow MHADA to utilize these flats for public housing. Rehabilitation buildings are ready for occupation.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/bombay-hc-allows-mhada-to-use-unclaimed-patra-chawl-flats-for-public-housing/130346600?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-213710/130346600.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}